    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Provide adequate shelter to all resident beneficiaries.\r\n\t\r\n\t\tProvide food, psycho-social counseling, clothing and access to medical care to resident and non-resident children.\r\n\t\r\n\t\tProvide occupational therapy to street-adolescents for rehabilitation purpose.\r\n\t\r\n\t\tProvide access to education to all beneficiaries: formal (in educational institute) and informal (conducted in the program), academic (school and college) and vocational (training institutes and workshops), long-term (long-term child care program) and short-term (rehab/reintegration program).\r\n\t\r\n\t\tEstablish and maintain a clear daily social structure with rules and regulations by which all resident beneficiaries abide.\r\n\t\r\n\t\tProvide job + give access to training (tailoring + literacy classes) to 15 women within the programs."
      },
      "ne": null
